
                  HUSKYLIB license notes.

HUSKYLIB is a part of the HUSKY Fidonet Software Project,
see http://husky.sourceforge.net for details.

HUSKYLIB is a library of commonly-used functions in the Husky project
and combines the following libraries: "SMAPI; Modified Squish MSGAPI"
and "FIDOCONFIG - library for fidonet configs".

Fidoconfig is distributed on the GNU LGPL terms

Squish MSGAPI0 is copyright 1991 by Scott J. Dudley on own license.
Scott J. Dudley agreed to change SMAPI license to LGPL at 2003 year.

